channel.title: [562] Project
channel.description:
To Start off, I'm Just going to add small things here and there, to keep the community up to date with what I've done.
Things Added (Gifs File are To large to upload....) - Pest Control - Duel Arena (not the tournament area, that is 20% done) - Magebank, PK Box, Fight Pits, other pk areas - Worlds 1 & 2, (1 is economy/skilling, 2 is PVP/Pking) - Port Sarim, boat control works. You can tele to appropriate places from the ships - Barrows Area (Currently Moving Npcs To Proper place when dug with spade, will be done in a weeks time) - Agility Wall, Taverly Dungeon - Canoe Traveling Well lets get started....posting just small things today.
Making Godswords and Dragon Fire Shield [IMG]http://i41.tinypic.com/2qcmnvc.gif[/img]
*Note* - Dragon Fire Shield Requires, hammer + Visage + anti-dragon shield, and the Required Smithing Level
Dagganoth Area, Aggresive... [IMG]http://i41.tinypic.com/dm5p1w.jpg[/img] [IMG]http://i41.tinypic.com/2lvzazm.jpg[/img] [IMG]http://i40.tinypic.com/10glctc.jpg[/img] [IMG]http://i41.tinypic.com/51t5pk.jpg[/img]
[IMG]http://i39.tinypic.com/2qn4pdj.gif[/img]
Added Almost Every item working, and currently done with 10% of all the Global Objects (ladders, doors, portals, ect)
Upload More As I go, not much time now, but will add more!
Thanks -Pure Slay
